title: Video: Kenny Jackett on Wolves v Boro
text:
PUBLISHED: October 22, 2015 1:00 pm LAST UPDATED: October 22, 2015 4:10 pm Video: Kenny Jackett on Wolves v Boro Watch boss Kenny Jackett's pre-match interview as Wolves look to arrest this week's slide at home to Middlesbrough on Saturday. Tweet 
Head coach Jackett has, so far, seen Wolves lose 4-2 away against Derby County on Sunday and 2-0 at home to Brentford last night. 
And promotion-chasing Boro are likely to present another stiff test at Molineux, although the visitors haven't scored in three games. More on this story:
